%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Smile%2C%20You%E2%80%99re%20With%20the%20PM%20and%20Your%20Train%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20on%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20nation%20has%20entrusted%20the%20Union%20government%20with%20the%20money%20collected%20from%20us%20through%20taxes%20and%20other%20levies.%20See%20how%20they%20spend%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Railways%20is%20one%20of%2019%20zones%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Railways.%20It%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20at%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20Terminus.%20Recently%2C%20they%20replied%20to%20an%20RTI%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20response%20below%2C%20on%20platforms%20in%20the%20Central%20Railway%20Zone%20alone%2C%20around%2020%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%206.25%20lakhs%20each%2C%20totalling%20to%20Rs%201.25%20crore.%20And%20another%2032%20odd%20%E2%80%9Ctemporary%E2%80%9D%20selfie%20booths%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20each%20(a%20modest%20Rs%2040%20lakh).%20This%20is%20essentially%20having%20a%20life-size%203D%20model%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20(they%20also%20have%20lower%20budget%20two-dimension%20life-size%20cutouts)%2C%20props%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20beside%20Modi%20and%20take%20selfies%20with%20their%20phone%20cameras.%20Circulated%20on%20social%20media%2C%20this%20is%20designed%20to%20pep%20up%20the%20popularity%20of%20our%20beloved%20PM.%20These%20props%20also%20have%20texts%20and%20images%20that%20highlight%20some%20flagship%20schemes%2C%20programmes%20or%20achievements%20by%20national%20or%20state%20agencies%2C%20for%20which%20the%20government%20seeks%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20cells