Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Balasore%20district%20involving%20the%20Coromandel%20Express%2C%20the%20Bengaluru-Howrah%20Superfast%20Express%20and%20a%20goods%20train%2C%20running%20on%20three%20separate%20tracks.%20The%20number%20of%20fatalities%20was%20never%20confirmed%2C%20but%20300%20people%20were%20seriously%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2013%2C%202022%2C%2012%20coaches%20of%20the%20Bikaner-Guwahati%20Express%20derailed%20in%20Alipurduar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20leaving%20nine%20dead%20and%2036%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2023%2C%202017%2C%20nine%20coaches%20of%20the%20Delhi-bound%20Kaifiyat%20Express%20derailed%20near%20Auraiya%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20leaving%20at%20least%2070%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2018%2C%202017%2C%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20the%20Puri-Haridwar%20Utkal%20Express%20derailed%2C%20killing%2023%20people%20and%20injuring%20nearly%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2020%2C%202016%2C%20the%20Indore-Patna%20Express%2019321%20derailed%20near%20Pukhrayan%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20killing%20at%20least%20150%20and%20injuring%20more%20than%20that%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2026%2C%202014%2C%20in%20the%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%20area%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Gorakhdham%20Express%20collided%20with%20a%20halted%20goods%20train%20near%20Khalilabad%20station%2C%20resulting%20in%2025%20fatalities%20and%20leaving%20more%20than%2050%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-on-indian-railways-expenses-ayushman-bharat-graft-diversion-of-pension-scheme-funds%5C%22%3ECAG%20on%20Indian%20Railways%E2%80%99%20Expenses%2C%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Graft%2C%20Diversion%20of%20Pension%20Scheme%20Funds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20blessed%20Railway%20Minister%2C%20the%20brief%20is%20clear.%20Millions%20visit%20railway%20stations%20every%20day.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20take%20political%20advantage%20of%20this%20captive%20crowd%2C%20to%20generate%20optics%20to%20promote%20the%20persona%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20his%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D.%20In%20an%20aeroplane%2C%20the%20passengers%20are%20forced%20to%20listen%20to%20government%20propaganda.%20Full%20marks%20to%20the%20Ministry%20for%20Aviation.%20(Thankfully%2C%20though%2C%20the%20selfie%20booth%20has%20not%20yet%20found%20its%20way%20into%20the%20aisle%20space.)%20Why%20are%20the%20Railways%20lagging%20behind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriorities%20are%20made%20clear%20to%20the%20minister.%20The%20budget%20for%20improving%20rail%20safety%2C%20or%20to%20provide%20enough%20sleeper%20berths%20and%20seats%20for%20passengers%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0be%20put%20into%20better%20use%20for%20much%20more%20nationalistic%20purposes%2C%20like%20erecting%20selfie%20booths%20to%20take%20pictures%20with%20Modi.%20I%20do%20not%20recall%20the%20expenditure%20head%20of%20selfie%20booths%20being%20spoken%20of%20in%20Parliament%20in%20the%202023%20Budget%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Railways%2C%20especially%20its%20deteriorating%20safety%20standards%2C%20is%20a%20terror%2C%20though%20it%20is%20the%20lifeline%20of%20our%20nation.%20But%20who%20cares%3F%20The%20minister%E2%80%99s%20boss%20will%20get%20happy%20only%20if%20he%20installs%20enough%20selfie%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20spending%20money%20for%20this%20nonsense%3F%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20put%20their%20lives%20at%20risk%20by%20travelling%20on%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndian%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Railways%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20goes%20through%20severe%20hardships%20to%20travel%20by%20train%20when%20the%20Railways%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20non-AC%20sleeper%20berths%20to%20favour%20luxurious%20AC%20accommodation%20for%20the%20rich%3F%20Yes%2C%20right%20again%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20government%20is%20without%20doubt%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuit-boot%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eki%20sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20It%20serves%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0the%20rich%2C%20and%20government%20funds%20are%20used%20only%20to%20prop%20up%20an%20insecure%20and%20inadequate%20narcissistic%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Koshy%20is%20a%20consultant%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20engineering%20sector.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22message-text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22block-kit-renderer%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703829168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29112023%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frailway-narendra-modi-selfie-booth%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20the%20blessed%20Railway%20Minister%2C%20the%20brief%20is%20clear.%20Millions%20visit%20railway%20stations%20every%20day.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20take%20political%20advantage%20of%20this%20captive%20crowd.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frailway-narendra-modi-selfie-booth%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Many%20Men%20in%20One%3A%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20BJP%20and%20the%20Play%20of%20Social%20Identities%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F29111106%2FUntitled-design-15-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPost-Modernist%20historians%20like%20Hayden%20White%20have%20argued%20that%20there%20are%20no%20stable%20significations%20in%20the%20world%20we%20live%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EErgo%2C%20the%20so-called%20stable%20nouns%20or%20identities%20that%20our%20words%20point%20to%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20merely%20chimeras%20in%20flux.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20they%20contend%2C%20what%20we%20dub%20%E2%80%98reality%E2%80%99%20is%20often%20only%20constituted%20by%20a%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20of%20narratives%20which%20owe%20no%20being%20or%20allegiance%20to%20any%20unshakable%20or%20rooted%20truths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20an%20intellectually%20engaging%20take%20on%20the%20often%20frustrating%20substance%20of%20human%20endeavours%2C%20but%20one%20that%20rather%20cleverly%20evades%20from%20a%20secure%20class%20position%20the%20quite%20determinable%20fact%20that%20such%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%2C%20be%20it%20of%20narratives%20or%20identities%2C%20is%20invariably%20linked%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20one%20form%20or%20another%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuman%20agents%20never%20cease%20to%20deploy%20what%20seem%20inconsistent%20narratives%20to%20obtain%20dominance%20over%20definitions%2C%20institutions%2C%20systems%20of%20governance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20when%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20was%20heard%20to%20make%20reference%20to%20his%20social%20identity%20in%20open%20session%20%E2%80%93%20a%20procedure%20frowned%20upon%20upon%20by%20constitutional%20etiquette%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20drawing%20upon%20a%20social%20resource%20that%20he%20felt%20at%20the%20time%20might%20have%20more%20traction%20among%20a%20television%20audience%20than%20his%20identities%20as%20vice-president%20of%20India%20and%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20mere%20idle%20%E2%80%98play%E2%80%99%20of%20an%20identity%20that%20but%20one%20cannily%20directed%20to%20a%20political%20purpose.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20of%20course%20few%20other%20nations%20that%20offer%20quite%20the%20same%20mind-boggling%20spread%20of%20identities%20as%20does%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20fact%20makes%20politics%20in%20India%20both%20endlessly%20frustrating%20and%20fascinating%20all%20at%20once.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELately%2C%20given%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20adroitness%20at%20sophistry%20(making%20false%20arguments%20stand%20for%20the%20lurking%20factual%20ones)%2C%20the%20forthcoming%20general%20elections%20are%20generating%20a%20most%20instructive%20skein%20of%20%E2%80%98takes%E2%80%99%20on%20who%20is%20who%20among%20contenders%20for%20state%20power%20at%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20man%20is%20now%20a%20pure%2C%20socially%20undifferentiated%20nationalist%2C%20and%20now%20a%20protagonist%20of%20this%20or%20that%20social%20group%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20not%20excluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20latest%20play%20is%20to%20foreground%20some%20demographic%20categories%20as%20the%20real%20four%20castes%20in%20India%2C%20do%20remember%20that%20he%20also%20gently%20reminds%20us%20now%20and%20again%20how%20he%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20numero%20uno%20of%20independent%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20back-and-forth%20of%20owning%20or%20disowning%20identities%20from%20time%20to%20time%20now%20can%20be%20seen%20to%20shape%20the%20canny%20calculations%20of%20segments%20of%20the%20electorate%20across%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20especially.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20a%20pretty%20ingenuous%20and%20politically%20telling%20sample%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%207%20o%E2%80%99clock%20evening%20bulletin%20of%20the%20electronic%20news%20channel%2C%20News%2024%2C%20in%20its%20popular%20programme%20%E2%80%98Mahol%20Kya%20Hai%20(what%20is%20the%20political%20weather%20like).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmimicry-jagdeep-dhankhar-kalyan-banerjee%5C%22%3EWe%20Were%20Created%20in%20Our%20Creator%E2%80%99s%20Image%20%E2%80%93%20Mimicry%20Is%20Our%20Manifest%20Destiny%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anchor%20in%20attendance%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20saffron%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ereinforced%20by%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalava%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20around%20his%20wrist%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20clear-enough%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20anxious%20to%20elicit%20from%20his%20exclusive%20Jat%20audience%20in%20Hapur%2C%20a%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20area%2C%20assent%20to%20the%20proposition%20that%20in%20mimicking%20Dhankhar%2C%20the%20political%20opposition%20had%20insulted%20all%20jats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImportant%20to%20note%20that%20this%20programme%20featured%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20late%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20whom%20Jats%20especially%20credit%20with%20having%20been%20not%20just%20their%20tallest%20leader%20%2C%20but%20of%20all%20agriculturists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStunningly%20came%20a%20retort%20that%20the%20only%20authentic%20Jats%20were%20the%20followers%20of%20that%20great%20departed%20leader%20and%2C%20then%2C%20of%20his%20lineage%20now%20led%20by%20his%20grandson%2C%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%3B%20those%20Jats%20who%20had%20their%20loyalties%20elsewhere%20were%20not%20Jats%20but%20Hindus!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nationalist%20right-wing%20of%20course%20continues%20to%20be%20frustrated%20by%20this%20most%20distressing%20schism%20among%20Indian%20Hindus%3A%20they%20re%20both%20Hindus%20with%20religious%20allegiances%20and%2C%20simultaneously%2C%20proud%20members%20of%20caste%20groups%20which%20they%20uphold%20as%20being%20more%20intimate%20to%20their%20concrete%20and%20grounded%20livelihoods%20than%20their%20rather%20more%20abstruse%20and%20undifferentiated%20religious%20oneness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20political%20conglomeration%20is%20thus%20constrained%20constantly%20to%20now%20deny%20the%20one%20and%20own%20the%20other%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20never%20quite%20able%20yet%20to%20extinguish%20the%20social%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20denominational%20as%20its%20monochromatic%20ideological%20purpose%20requires.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20dance%20of%20necessity%20of%20course%20is%20distorted%20by%20grave%20and%20in-your-face%20contradictions%20which%20often%20the%20best%20of%20their%20sophistry%20fails%20to%20eschew.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%2C%20for%20example%2C%20asked%20why%20Dhankhar%E2%80%99s%20proud%20social%20allegiance%20did%20not%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20globally%20decorated%20Jat%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20shamefully%20humiliated%20throughout%20their%20prolonged%20protest%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20alleged%20%E2%80%98sexual%20harassment%E2%80%99%20by%20th