Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20nationalist%20right-wing%2C%20thus%2C%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20it%20must%20both%20press%20into%20political%20service%20social%2Fcaste%20identities%20as%20do%20the%20opposition%2C%20but%20also%20oppose%20the%20holding%20of%20a%20caste-census%2C%20lest%20a%20social-denominational%20reality%20come%20to%20overwhelm%20its%20project%20of%20religious%20consolidation%20to%20the%20exclusion%20of%20all%20concrete%20social%20realities%20and%20imperatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20is%20comforting%20that%20the%20opposition%20seems%20to%20have%20largely%20succeeded%20in%20quelling%20the%20canny%20narrative%20of%20insult%20to%20Jat%20identity%20via%20the%20mimicking%20of%20Dhankhar%20by%20forcefully%20foregrounding%20the%20more%20real%20and%20consequential%20issues%20of%20ingress%20of%20undesirables%20into%20parliament%2C%20the%20undemocratic%2Funconstitutional%20refusal%20of%20the%20executive%20to%20take%20parliament%20into%20confidence%20on%20it%2C%20and%20the%20unprecedented%20ejection%20of%20practically%20all%20opposition%20lawmakers%20%E2%80%93%20designed%20to%20serve%20two%20governmental%20purposes%3A%20one%2C%20to%20deflect%20from%20accountability%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20to%20avert%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20intruder%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20House%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fpratap-simhas-path-to-power-paved-with-provocation%5C%22%3Efacilitated%20by%20a%20BJP%20member%20of%20the%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20to%20facilitate%20the%20passage%20of%20more%20than%20one%20potentially%20citizen-retrograde%20legislation%20with%20no%20opposition%20to%20counter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20top%20it%20al%2C%20consider%20that%20while%20the%20entire%20opposition%20has%20been%20thrown%20out%2C%20the%20one%20parliamentarian%20whose%20say-so%20enabled%20the%20intruders%20to%20enter%20parliament