gation%2C%20and%20the%20officers%20are%20working%20to%20determine%20the%20motive%20of%20this%20incident%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20not%20known%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Surrey%20Police%20have%20not%20confirmed%20any%20link%20of%20the%20attack%20to%20recent%20threats%20received%20by%20the%20Lakshmi%20Narayan%20Mandir%20in%20Surrey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20November%2C%20India-origin%20Canadian%20member%20of%20Parliament%20Chandra%20Arya%20shared%20a%20purported%20video%20of%20Pro%20Khalistani%20supporters%20in%20Surrey%20claiming%20they%20want%20to%20create%20trouble%20at%20the%20Hindu%20Lakshmi%20Narayan%20Mandir%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BLast%20week%2C%20Khalistan%20supporters%20verbally%20abused%20a%20Sikh%20family%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20BC%2C%20according%20to%20some%20reports.%20Now%20it%20appears%20the%20same%20Khalistan%20group%20wants%20to%20create%20trouble%20at%20the%20Hindu%20Lakshmi%20Narayan%20Mandir%20in%20Surrey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20that%20Hindu%20temples%20have%20remained%20targets%20for%20attacks%20over%20the%20past%20years%2C%20Arya%20noted%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHindu%20temples%20have%20been%20attacked%20many%20times%20during%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%20Hate%20crimes%20are%20being%20committed%20against%20Hindu-Canadians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20was%20vandalised%20in%20Canada%20by%20extremist%20elements%20with%20Khalistan%20referendum%20posters%20in%20August%20this%20year.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20BAPS%20Swaminarayan%20temple%20was%20vandalised%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti%20in%20Windsor%2C%20in%20Canada's%20Ontario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20February%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Canada's%20Mississauga%20was%20vandalised%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti.%20In%20January%2C%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Brampton%20was%20defaced%20with