%20Index.%20The%20milestone%20came%20as%20shares%20of%20L'Oreal%20SA%2C%20the%20beauty%20products%20empire%20founded%20by%20her%20grandfather%2C%20rose%20to%20a%20record%20high%2C%20with%20the%20stock%20set%20for%20its%20best%20year%20since%201998.%20She's%20the%2012th-richest%20person%20in%20the%20world%2C%20just%20behind%20Mexico's%20Carlos%20Slim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20gain%2C%20Bettencourt%20Meyers'%20fortune%20is%20still%20significantly%20less%20than%20that%20of%20French%20compatriot%20Bernard%20Arnault%2C%20founder%20of%20luxury%20goods%20purveyor%20LVMH%20Moet%20Hennessy%20Louis%20Vuitton%20SE%2C%20who%20is%20second%20in%20the%20global%20ranking%20with%20%24179%20billion.%20France's%20growing%20domination%20of%20luxury%20retail%20has%20spawned%20several%20other%20ultra-rich%20families%2C%20including%20the%20clan%20behind%20Hermes%20International%20SCA%2C%20who%20have%20amassed%20Europe's%20largest%20family%20fortune%2C%20and%20the%20Wertheimer%20brothers%20who%20own%20Chanel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reclusive%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%2C%2070%2C%20is%20vice-chair%20of%20the%20board%20of%20L'Oreal%2C%20a%20globe-spanning%20241%20billion%20pounds%20(%24268%20billion)%20company%20in%20which%20she%20and%20her%20family%20are%20the%20single%20biggest%20shareholders%20with%20a%20stake%20of%20nearly%2035%25.%20Her%20sons%2C%20Jean-Victor%20Meyers%20and%20Nicolas%20Meyers%2C%20are%20also%20directors.%20Run%20by%20executives%20from%20outside%20the%20family%20for%20decades%2C%20the%20firm%20was%20founded%20in%201909%20by%20Bettencourt%20Meyers'%20chemist%20grandfather%2C%20Eugene%20Schueller%2C%20to%20produce%20and%20sell%20a%20hair%20dye%20he%20had%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBettencourt%20Meyers%20keeps%20her%20life%20private%2C%20shunning%20the%20glitzy%20social%20life%20sought%20by%20many%20the%20world's%20wealthy.%20She%20has%20written%20two%20books%20-%20a%20five-volume%20study%20of%20the%20Bible%20and%20a%20genealogy%20of%20the%20Greek%20gods%20-%20and%20is%20known%20for%20playing%20piano%20for%20hours%20every%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStock%20Rebound%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20only%20child%2C%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%20came%20into%20her%20wealth%20following%20the%202017%20death%20of%20her%20mother%2C%20Liliane%20Bettencourt%2C%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20an%20at%20times%20contentious%20relationship.%20A%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20aughts%20grew%20from%20a%20family%20feud%20to%20a%20political%20scandal%20that%20centered%20on%20whether%20the%20elderly%20mother%20was%20fit%20to%20manage%20the%20family's%20wealth.%20Last%20month%2C%20Netflix%20Inc.%20came%20out%20with%20a%20three-part%20documentary%2C%20L'Affaire%20Bettencourt%2C%20relating%20the%20saga%20that%20featured%20a%20former%20French%20president%20and%20secret%20recordings%20made%20by%20a%20butler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL'Oreal%20grew%20rapidly%20in%20the%20decade%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20pandemic%20but%20took%20a%20hit%20during%20the%20health%20crisis%20when%20people%20under%20lockdown%20used%20less%20makeup.%20That%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20rapid%20rebound%20as%20consumers%20splurged%20on%20luxury%20items%2C%20sending%20the%20shares%20up%2035%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20could%20rise%20another%2012%25%20over%20the%20next%20year%20as%20its%20product%20and%20geographic%20diversity%20shows%20resilience%2C%20according%20to%20Consumer%20Edge%20Research%20analyst%20Brett%20Cooper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBettencourt%20Meyers%20also%20chairs%20her%20family's%20holding%20company%2C%20Tethys%2C%20which%20has%20the%20L'Oreal%20stake.%20Her%20husband%2C%20Jean-Pierre%20Meyers%2C%20is%20chief%20executive.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20two%20set%20up%20subsidiary%20Tethys%20Invest%20SAS%2C%20which%20bets%20on%20areas%20that%20don't%20compete%20with%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20stated%20intention%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20long-term%20investments%20in%20entrepreneurial%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tethys%20Invest%20is%20Alexandre%20Benais%2C%20a%20former%20Lazard%20Ltd.%20investment%20banker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETethys%20Invest%20recently%20acquired%20a%20stake%20in%20French%20insurance%20broker%20April%20Group.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20bought%20into%20decade-old%20fashion%20brand%20Sezane%2C%20and%20has%20also%20invested%20in%20French%20private%20hospital%20operator%20Elsan.%20The%20firm%20is%20partly%20funded%20by%20L'Oreal%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703824260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9bah2hvg_francoise-bettencourt-meyers-bloombeg_625x300_29_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcosmetics-brand-loreal-heir-francoise-bettencourt-meyers-becomes-1st-woman-to-hit-100-billion-fortune-4761925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Francoise%20Bettencourt%20Meyers%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20amass%20a%20%24100%20billion%20fortune%2C%20marking%20another%20milestone%20for%20the%20heiress%20and%20for%20France's%20expanding%20fashion%20and%20cosmetics%20industries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcosmetics-brand-loreal-heir-francoise-bettencourt-meyers-becomes-1st-woman-to-hit-100-billion-fortune-4761925%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcosmetics-brand-loreal-heir-francoise-bettencourt-meyers-becomes-1st-woman-to-hit-100-billion-fortune-4761925%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcosmetics-brand-loreal-heir-francoise-bettencourt-meyers-becomes-1st-woman-to-hit-100-billion-fortune-4761925%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22t