C%20military%20bases%20along%20the%20Gaza%20border%2C%20and%20Kibbutzim.%20Witnesses%20described%20graphic%20scenes%20of%20women%20being%20raped%20and%20killed%20at%20different%20locations%20along%20Route%20232%2C%20the%20highway%20where%20Gal%20Abdush's%20body%20was%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteer%20medics%20and%20soldiers%20reported%20discovering%20more%20than%2030%20bodies%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20in%20a%20state%20similar%20to%20Gal%20Abdush's--legs%20spread%2C%20clothes%20torn%20off%2C%20and%20signs%20of%20abuse%20in%20their%20genital%20areas%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NYT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20states%20that%20The%20Times%20viewed%20disturbing%20photographs%20and%20videos%2C%20including%20one%20woman's%20corpse%20with%20nails%20driven%20into%20her%20thighs%20and%20groin.%20Another%20video%2C%20provided%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20showed%20two%20dead%20soldiers%20at%20a%20base%20near%20Gaza%20who%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20shot%20directly%20in%20their%20genital%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20denied%20accusations%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20leading%20to%20outrage%20among%20Israeli%20activists.%20United%20Nations%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20and%20UN%20Women%20faced%20criticism%20for%20not%20acknowledging%20the%20accusations%20promptly%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20police%2C%20acknowledging%20challenges%20during%20the%20chaotic%20events%20of%20October%207%2C%20revealed%20they%20were%20not%20initially%20focused%20on%20collecting%20forensic%20evidence%20from%20women's%20bodies.%20Chaos%2C%20grief%2C%20and%20religious%20duties%20led%20to%20hasty%20burials%2C%20with%20many%20bodies%20remaining%20unexamined.%20The%20lack%20of%20autopsies%20and%20crime%20scene%20examinations%20has%20left%20families%20searching%20for%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20faced%20hurdles%20in%20collecting%20forensic%20evidence%2C%20typical%20in%20cases%20of%20widespread%20sexual%20violence%20during%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdil%20Haque%2C%20a%20Rutgers%20law%20professor%20and%20war%20crimes%20expert%2C%20explained%20the%20challenges%2C%20noting%20that%20armed%20conflicts%20prioritise%20safety%20over%20building%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArmed%20conflict%20is%20so%20chaotic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20very%20often%20sex%20crime%20cases%20will%20be%20prosecuted%20years%20later%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20testimony%20from%20victims%20and%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20eyewitness%20might%20not%20even%20know%20the%20name%20of%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20they%20can%20testify%20as%2C%20'I%20saw%20a%20woman%20being%20raped%20by%20this%20armed%20group%2C'%20that%20can%20be%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20NYT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20witness%2C%20named%20Sapir%2C%20provided%20graphic%20testimony%2C%20describing%20the%20brutalisation%20of%20women%20by%20heavily%20armed%20gunmen.%20She%20recalled%20witnessing%20the%20rape%20and%20killing%20of%20at%20least%20five%20women%2C%20emphasising%20the%20chaos%20and%20brutality%20of%20the%20attackers.%20Sapir's%20account%20was%20supported%20by%20photographs%20of%20her%20hiding%20place%20and%20her%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2015%20meters%20from%20her%20hiding%20place%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20saw%20motorcycles%2C%20cars%20and%20trucks%20pulling%20up.%20She%20said%20that%20she%20saw%20%26quot%3Babout%20100%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20most%20of%20them%20dressed%20in%20military%20fatigues%20and%20combat%20boots%2C%20a%20few%20in%20dark%20sweatsuits%2C%20getting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20vehicles.%20She%20said%20the%20men%20congregated%20along%20the%20road%20and%20passed%20between%20them%20assault%20rifles%2C%20grenades%2C%20small%20missiles%20--%20and%20badly%20wounded%20women%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20an%20assembly%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20victim%20she%20said%20she%20saw%20was%20a%20young%20woman%20with%20copper-colour%20hair%2C%20blood%20running%20down%20her%20back%2C%20pants%20pushed%20down%20to%20her%20knees.%20One%20man%20pulled%20her%20by%20the%20hair%20and%20made%20her%20bend%20over.%20Another%20penetrated%20her%2C%20Sapir%20said%2C%20and%20every%20time%20she%20flinched%2C%20he%20plunged%20a%20knife%20into%20her%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20then%20watched%20another%20woman%20%26quot%3Bshredded%20into%20pieces.%26quot%3B%20While%20one%20terrorist%20raped%20her%2C%20she%20said%2C%20another%20pulled%20out%20a%20box%20cutter%20and%20sliced%20off%20her%20breast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20continues%20to%20rape%20her%2C%20and%20the%20other%20throws%20her%20breast%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20and%20they%20play%20with%20it%2C%20throw%20it%2C%20and%20it%20falls%20on%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NYT%20quoted%20Sapir%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20men%20sliced%20her%20face%20and%20then%20the%20woman%20fell%20out%20of%20view.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20saw%20three%20other%20women%20raped%20and%20terrorists%20carrying%20the%20severed%20heads%20of%20three%20more%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESapir%20provided%20photographs%20of%20her%20hiding%20place%20and%20her%20wounds%2C%20and%20police%20officials%20have%20stood%20by%20her%20testimony%20and%20released%20a%20video%20of%20her%2C%20with%20her%20face%20blurred%2C%20recounting%20some%20of%20what%20she%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20witnesses%2C%20like%20Raz%20Cohen%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NYT%20report%2C%20a%20young%20Israeli%20who%20had%20also%20attended%20the%20rave%20and%20had%20worked%20recently%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20training%20Congolese%20soldiers%20--%20said%20that%20he%20was%20hiding%20in%20a%20dried-up%20streambed.%20It%20provided%20some%20cover%20from%20the%20assailants%20combing%20the%20area%20and%20shooting%20anyone%20they%20found%2C%20he%20said%20in%20an%20hour-and-a-half%20interview%20in%20a%20Tel%20Aviv%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaybe%2040%20yards%20in%20front%20of%20him%2C%20he%20recalled%2C%20a%20white%20van%20pulled%20up%20and%20its%20doors%20flew%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20then%20saw%20five%20men%2C%20wearing%20civilian%20clothes%2C%20all%20carrying%20knives%20and%20one%20carrying%20a%20hammer%2C%20dragging%20a%20woman%20across%20the%20ground.%20She%20was%20young%2C%20naked%20and%20screaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20gather%20around%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20standing%20up.%20They%20start%20raping%20her.%20I%20saw%20the%20men%20standing%20in%20a%20half%20circle%20around%20her.%20One%20penetrates%20her.%20She%20screams.%20I%20still%20remember%20her%20voice%2C%20screams%20without%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20one%20of%20them%20raises%20a%20knife%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20they%20just%20slaughtered%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2C%20account%20cited%20by%20the%20NYT%20report%20was%20of%20Shoam%20Gueta%2C%20who%20also%20recounted%20horrifying%20scenes%20of%20women%20being%20raped%20and%20slaughtered.%20Volunteer%20emergency%20medical%20technicians%20described%20discovering%20bodies%20with%20signs%20of%20sexual%20assault%20at%20the%20rave%20site%20and%20in%20kibbutzim%2C%20regretting%20their%20inability%20to%20document%20more%20due%20to%20religious%20rules%20and%20the%20need%20for%20respect%20for%20the%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20Israeli%20police%20continue%20to%20uncover%20evidence%20of%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Superintendent%2C%20Moshe%20Fintzy%2C%20highlighted%20the%20recovery%20of%20videos%20showing%20women%20being%20brutalised%2C%20emphasising%20the%20dual%20forces%20of%20anti-Semitism%20and%20misogyny%20at%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn