Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jerusalem%2C%20families%20of%20hostages%20still%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20again%20rallied%20for%20their%20release%2C%20and%20a%20kibbutz%20announced%20that%20a%2070-year-old%20US-Israeli%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20oldest%20woman%20held%20captive%20had%20died%20in%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdevastated%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20news%20Judith%20Weinstein%20Haggai%20was%20dead%2C%20and%20pledged%20that%20Washington%20will%20%26quot%3Bnot%20stop%20working%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20ally%20Israel%20to%20bring%20the%20remaining%20hostages%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%2C%20which%20started%20with%20Hamas's%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20has%20left%20much%20of%20northern%20Gaza%20in%20ruins%20while%20the%20battlefront%20has%20shifted%20ever%20further%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20besieged%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20said%20it%20had%20deployed%20an%20additional%20brigade%20to%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20hometown%20of%20Hamas's%20Gaza%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%2C%20where%20AFP%20correspondents%20reported%20sustained%20air%20and%20artillery%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20society%20reported%20that%20shelling%20had%20killed%20at%20least%2010%20people%20near%20the%20city's%20Al-Amal%20hospital%2C%20an%20area%20where%20it%20said%20about%2014%2C000%20people%20are%20sheltering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20Thursday%2C%20Hamas-run%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry%20said%2020%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children%2C%20and%20dozens%20wounded%20in%20shelling%20of%20the%20Shaboura%20camp%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20October%207%20attack%20which%20left%20about%201%2C140%20people%20dead%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20Israeli