0Waleed%20Mohammed%20Aeid%20voiced%20his%20pain%20and%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20told%20us%20to%20go%20to%20Rafah%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20want%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%3F%20To%20go%20live%20in%20the%20streets%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20neighbourhood%20here%20was%20evacuated.%20They%20bombed%20the%20school%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20leave%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20anywhere%20else%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Israeli%20siege%20imposed%20after%20October%207%2C%20following%20years%20of%20crippling%20blockade%2C%20has%20deprived%20Gazans%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20fuel%20and%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20severe%20shortages%20have%20been%20only%20sporadically%20eased%20by%20humanitarian%20aid%20convoys%20entering%20primarily%20via%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20said%20Thursday%20it%20had%20given%20preliminary%20approval%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%20island%20nation%20of%20Cyprus%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmaritime%20lifeline%26quot%3B%20to%20ship%20aid%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20basic%20authorisation%20to%20use%20this%20route%2C%20but%20there%20are%20still%20some%20logistical%20problems%20that%20are%20waiting%20to%20be%20solved%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesman%20Lior%20Haiat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20many%20Palestinians%20displaced%2C%2028-year-old%20Iman%20al-Masry%2C%20recently%20gave%20birth%20to%20quadruplets%20in%20southern%20Gaza%20after%20fleeing%20her%20home%20in%20the%20devastated%20north.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arduous%20journey%20%26quot%3Baffected%20my%20pregnancy%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said%2C%20recounting%20that%20she%20gave%20birth%20by%20C-section%20on%20December%2018%20to%20two%20girls%20and%20two%20boys%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20was%20too%20fragile%20to%20leave%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20very%20slim%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20speaking%20in%20a%20school