.%20In%20the%20interview%20footage%20posted%20on%20the%20Formula%20One%20legend's%20website%20by%20his%20family%2C%20the%20seven-time%20world%20champion%20explained%20the%20secret%20behind%20his%20historic%20records%20was%20that%20he%20has%20found%20new%20ways%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecords%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20doubts%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20not%20be%20over%20confident%20-%20to%20be%20skeptical%2C%20to%20look%20for%20improvements%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20world%20champion%20said%20in%20the%20clip%20that%20was%20filmed%20on%20October%2030%2C%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20always%20felt%20I%20am%20not%20good%20enough%2C%20I%20have%20to%20work%2C%20and%20that%20was%20one%20part%20of%20the%20recipe%20that%20made%20me%20what%20I%20became.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwenty-one%20years%20no%20championship%20with%20Ferrari%2C%20four%20years%20myself%20failing%2C%20then%20finally%2C%20in%20a%20great%20race%2C%20to%20achieve%20it%2C%20win%20the%20world%20championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20respected%20guy%20in%20all%20those%20years%20was%20definitely%20Mika%20Hakkinen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BGreat%20fights%2C%20but%20stable%20private%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703820840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fgou9avn_michael-schumacher-afp_625x300_17_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Fmichael-schumacher-driven-in-mercedes-amg-car-to-stimulate-brain-new-report-claims-on-10th-anniversary-of-f1-greats-accident-4760203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Formula%201%20legend%20Michael%20Schumacher%2C%20a%20seven-time%20world%20champion%2C%20suffered%20an%20accident%20while%20skiing%20in%20the%20French%20Alps%20ski%20resort%20of%20Meribel%20on%20December%2029%2C%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com