n%20Santiniketan%2C%20Hazra%20set%20up%20a%20booth%2C%20encouraging%20discontented%20BJP%20members%20and%20dissatisfied%20workers%20to%20express%20their%20grievances%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHazra%20has%20had%20run-ins%20with%20the%20party%20leadership%20both%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20professor%20at%20Visva-Bharati%20University%2C%20he%20had%20first%20been%20elected%20in%202014%20from%20the%20Bolpur%20constituency%20on%20a%20TMC%20ticket%2C%20having%20defeated%20the%20CPI(M)%20by%20over%202.5%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20had%20then%20alleged%20being%20disallowed%20from%20taking%20independent%20decisions%20due%20to%20the%20political%20influence%20of%20powerful%20party%20leaders%20from%20his%20region%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20being%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20in%20January%202019%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20got%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20Jadavpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20but%20lost%20to%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20Mimi%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202020%2C%20Hazra%20was%20appointed%20as%20national%20secretary%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20Rahul%20Sinha%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20reappointed%20Hazra%20as%20national%20secretary%20for%20a%20second%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20developments%20in%20West%20Bengal%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20turmoil%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Karnataka%20unit%2C%20which%20is%20also%20facing%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20from%20within%2C%20reflecting%20apparent%20infighting%20between%20two%20factions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fkarnataka%2Fbjp-mla-says-yediyurappa-was-involved-in-rs-40000cr-corruption-in-covid-management%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Basangouda%20Patil%20Yatnal%2C%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20accused%20former%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%20of%20acquiring%20face%20masks%20at%20an%20inflated%20rate%2C%20resulting%20in%20irregularities%20totaling%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYatnal%20also%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20involved%20in%20trying%20to%20conceal%20the%20alleged%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20urged%20Yatnal%20to%20submit%20all%20pertinent%20documents%20to%20the%20Justice%20Nagamohan%20Das%20Commission%2C%20which%20was%20investigating%20allegations%20related%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9840%25%20commission%E2%80%99%20allegations%20made%20by%20contractors%20during%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20P.%20Rajeev%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20party%20had%20taken%20note%20of%20certain%20recent%20developments%20and%20would%20not%20tolerate%20any%20activities%20that%20cause%20damage%20to%20its%20dignity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndoor%20discussions%20cannot%20be%20disclosed.%20What%20I%20can%20say%20is%20that%20the%20party%20will%20not%20tolerate%20any%20activities%20that%20cause%20damage%20to%20its%20dignity.%20Serious%20discussions%20have%20happened%20within%20four%20walls%2C%20and%20our%20central%20leadership%20will%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision%20at%20an%20appropriate%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-tolerate-damage-to-party-