u%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703770167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F28185638%2FVijayakanth.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvijayakanth-no-more%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vijayakanth%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Captain%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20on%20ventilation%20support%20shortly%20before%20his%20death%20on%20Thursday%20morning.%20He%20had%20been%20discharged%20from%20an%20earlier%20stint%20in%20hospital%20two%20weeks%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvijayakanth-no-more%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Arrests%20Likely%20in%20Nijjar%20Assassination%20Case%20by%20Canadian%20Police%3A%20The%20Globe%20and%20Mail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29175202%2Fmodi-biden-trudeau.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20leading%20Canadian%20daily%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Globe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20two%20men%20who%20have%20allegedly%20killed%20a%20US-Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20separatist%20Sikh%20leader%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle-rcmp-expected-to-make-arrests-soon-in-sikh-leaders-slaying%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20likely%20to%20be%20arrested%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20developments%20that%20are%20set%20to%20increase%20troubles%20being%20faced%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20accusations%20of%20%E2%80%98transnational%20repression%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20targeting%20of%20US%20and%20Canadian%20citizens%20on%20their%20soil%2C%20reports%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthree%20sources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Globe%20and%20Mail%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20suspected%20killers%20never%20left%20Canada%20after%20Mr.%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20slaying%20and%20have%20been%20under%20police%20surveillance%20for%20months.%20Two%20of%20the%20sources%20said%20the%20RCMP%20(Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police)%20are%20expected%20to%20make%20arrests%20and%20lay%20charges%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20charges%20and%20alleged%20links%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Indian%20government%E2%80%9D%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20made%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sources%20have%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolice%20will%20explain%20the%20alleged%20assassins%E2%80%99%20involvement%20and%20that%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20when%20charges%20are%20laid%20against%20the%20two%20men.%20The%20Globe%20is%20not%20identifying%20the%20sources%20because%20they%20were%20not%20authorised%20to%20discuss%20national-security%20and%20police%20matters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20known%2C%20adds%20the%20paper%20whether%20arrests%20of%20any%20other%20%E2%80%9Csuspected%20accomplices%20in%20the%20slaying%E2%80%9D%20are%20expected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cvideo%20footage%20and%20witness%20accounts%2C%20that%20at%20least%20six%20men%20and%20two%20vehicles%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnikhil-gupta-pannun-assassination-plot-documents%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Nick%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Money%20Courier%20and%20a%20Hitman%3A%20What%20New%20Documents%20Say%20About%20The%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20and%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20ties%20took%20a%20hit%20when%20Justin%20Trudeau%20first%20made%20accusations%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20on%20September%2018%20in%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20earlier%20this%20year.%20India%20had%20strongly%20denied%20his%20charges%20then.%20But%20after%20a%20damning%20criminal%20indictment%20by%20the%20United%20States%20was%20unsealed%20(made%20public)%2C%20alleging%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20arrested%20and%20detained%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20in%20June%2C%20%E2%80%9Callegedly%20arranged%20the%20murder%20for%20hire%20of%20the%20U.S.-based%20Sikh%20activist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20general%20counsel%20for%20the%20New%20York-based%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%20had%20said%20it%20will%20cooperate%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20stopped%20denying%20charges%20directly%20as%20it%20had%20done%20earlier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703766605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29175202%2Fmodi-biden-trudeau.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ftwo-arrests-likely-in-nijjar-assassination-case-by-canadian-police-the-globe-and-daily-mail%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20troubles%20bound%20to%20increase%20as%20sources%20have%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolice%20will%20explain%20the%20alleged%20assassins%E2%80%99%20involvement%20and%20that%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20when%20charges%20are%20laid%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ftwo-arrests-likely-in-nijjar-assassination-case-by-canadian-police-the-globe-and-daily-mail%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Has%20Outdone%20Its%20Backers%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Britain%2C%20in%20Reducing%20Cities%20to%20Rubble%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_Anti-Israel_Protest_Washington_DC_USA_01949_32857528933.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20indiscriminate%2C%20relentless%20and%20above%20all%2C%20unopposed%20aerial%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20over%20the%20past%2080-odd%20days%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20can%20be%20likened%20to%20hunting%20big%20game%20in%20a%20zoo%20or%20game%20reserve.%20It%20exceeds%20the%20ghastly%20redux%20of%20what%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20backers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20US%20and%20Britain%20%E2%80%93%20executed%20during%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20world%20war%2C%20by%20carpet%20bombing%20the%20German%20city%20of%20Dresden%20and%2C%20like%20Gaza%2C%20reducing%20it%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20four%20consecutive%20raids%20between%20February%2013-15%2C%201945%20by%20772%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20(RAF)%20%C2%A0heavy%20bombers%20and%20527%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Army%20Air%20Force%20(USAAF)%20dropped%20more%20than%203%2C900%20tons%20of%20ordnance%20and%20incendiary%20devices%20on%20Dresden%2C%20capital%20of%20the%20German%20state%20of%20Saxony%2C%20killing%20over%2025%2C000%20people.%20Like%20the%20RAF%20and%20the%20USAAF%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20nearly%20eight%20decades%20later%20faced%20no%20airborne%20resistance%20in%20fulfilling%20its%20blood%20lust%20by%20raining%20death%20and%20destruction%20on%20an%20industrial%20scale%2C%20largely%20upon%20a%20civilian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequent%20reports%20and%20analyses%20%E2%80%9Cjustified%E2%80%9D%20the%20Dresden%20bombings%2C%20much%20like%20the%20IDF%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20today%2C%20on%20grounds%20of%20strategic%20and%20political%20exigency.%20But%2C%20over%20intervening%20years%20%2Cjurists%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%20had%20maintained%20that%20indiscriminately%20pounding%20Dresden%20constituted%20a%20heinous%20war%20crime%2C%20as%20the%20ongoing%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20was%20already%20being%20defined%20almost%20daily%20in%20world%20capitals%2C%20including%20London%20and%20Washington%2C%20by%20millions%20of%20protesting%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20assessments%2C%20had%20conducted%20strategic%20bombing%20missions%20over%20Gaza%2C%20dropping%20over%2029%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20air-to-ground%20munitions%20across%20a%20365%20sq.%20km%20area%2C%20or%20nearly%2080%20lbs%20of%20killer%20ordnance%20per%20sq.%20km.%20This%20was%20aimed%20egregiously%20into%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20densely%20populated%20region%20that%20includes%20eight%20refugee%20camps%20and%20a%20population%20density%20of%206%2C507%20persons%20per%20sq.%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20these%20unremitting%20IDF%20air%20strikes%20have%20significantly%20added%20to%20the%20overall%20Palestinian%20death%20toll%2C%20which%20currently%20totals%20around%2021%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20some%206%2C000%20children.%20Another%2055%2C000-odd%20Palestinians%20had%20been%20wounded%2C%20with%20little%20or%20no%20recourse%20to%20medical%20assistance%2C%20or%20hope%20of%20any%20kind%20in%20a%20war-ravaged%20and%20besieged%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20human%20rights%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-war-in-gaza-is-reshaping-geopolitics%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20War%20in%20Gaza%20Is%20Reshaping%20Geopolitics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20December%2014%20report%2C%20CNN%2C%20quoting%20unnamed%20US%20intelligence%20sources%2C%20claimed%20that%2045%25%20of%20this%20killer%20ordnance%20delivered%20aerially%2C%20comprised%20unguided%20bunker%20busters%2C%20or%20free-fall%20%E2%80%98dumb%20bombs%E2%80%99%20that%20were%20not%20fitted%20with%20any%20guidance%20systems.%20In%20its%20website%20report%20it%20declared%20that%20if%20the%20IDF%20was%20employing%20unguided%20munitions%20at%20the%20rate%2C%20like%20the%20US%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20believes%20it%20was%2C%20then%20it%20simply%20%E2%80%98undercut%E2%80%99%20Tel%20Aviv%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20%C2%A0trying%20to%20minimise%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNN%20further%20went%20on%20to%20state%20that%20the%20US%20had%20supplied%20Israel%20some%203%2C000%20of%20these%20joint%20direct%20attack%20munitions%20(JDAMs)%20since%20October%207%20after%20the%20Gaza%20offensive%20began%2C%20following%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20cross-border%20raid%20on%20multiple%20Israeli%20targets%2C%20in%20which%20some%201%2C200%20people%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20hundreds%20of%20others%20kidnapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20the%20blast%20from%20these%201%2C000-2%2C000-odd%20pound%20JDAMs%20in%20open%20spaces%20meant%20%E2%80%98instant%20death%E2%80%99%20for%20anyone%20within%20a%2030-metre%20radius%3B%20lethal%20fragmentation%20from%20them%20extended%20around%20365m.%20In%20an%20October%2031%20strike%20on%20the%20urban%20refugee%20camp%20of%20Jabaliya%20at%20the%20northern%20end%20of%20the%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20a%202%2C000-pound%20unguided%20JDAM%20had%20instantly%20killed%20over%20100%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailed%20accounts%20from%20the%20battle%20zone%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20IDF%20frequently%20dive-bombed%20its%20ground%20targets%20with%20JDAMs%2C%20rendering%20their%20impact%20even%20more%20lethal.%C2%A0%20Marc%20Garlasco%2C%20a%20former%20Pentagon%20official%20and%20United%20Nations%20war%20crimes%20investigator%20told%20the%20Associated%20Press%20(AP)%20recently%20that%20these%20JDAMS%20turn%20%E2%80%98earth%20to%20liquid%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98pancaked%20entire%20buildings%E2%80%99.%20Other%20Western%20military%20analysts%20concurred%20that%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20Israel%20was%20using%20these%20dumb%20bombs%20was%20%E2%80%98contributing%20significantly%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20soaring%20Palestinian%20death%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%2C%20however%2C%20in%20the%20fog%20of%20war%2C%20the%20high%20level%20of%20secrecy%20prevailing%20over%20the%20conflict%20and%20lack%20of%20access%20provided%20by%20Israel%20to%20independent%20news%20reporters%2C%20the%20exact%20nature%20of%20these%20killer%20bombs.%20But%20experts%20claimed%20some%20of%20them%20to%20be%20US-origin%20M117%E2%80%99s%20that%20were%20used%20extensively%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20and%20thereafter%20during%20Operation%20Desert%20Storm%20against%20the%20Iraqi%20military%2C%20in%20the%20early%201990%E2%80%99s%2C%20with%20devastating%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNN%20and%20other%20US%20media%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20US%20had%20provided%20Israel%20with%20assorted%20unguided%20bombs%2C%20including%205%2C000%20Mk82s%20and%20its%20variants.%20These%20were%20500-pound%20low-drag%2C%20general%20purpose%20aircraft%20bombs%20containing%20around%20200%20lbs%20of%20high%20explosive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20bad%20enough%20to%20be%20using%20these%20weapons%20(bombs)%20when%20they%20are%20precisely%20hitting%20their%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Brian%20Castner%2C%20a%20weapons%20investigator%20and%20ordnance%20expert%20with%20Amnesty%20International%20told%20CNN.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20a%20massive%20civilian%20harm%20problem%20if%20they%20do%20not%20have%20that%20accuracy%2C%20and%20if%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20determine%20whether%20the%20bomb%20is%20actually%20landing%20where%20the%20IDF%20intended%20it%20to%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestine-palestinians-and-the-western-liberals-burden%5C%22%3EPalestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20widespread%20criticism%2C%20including%20from%20United%20Nations%20bodies%2C%20the%20US%20has%20quietly%20continued%20to%20supply%20materiel%2C%20including%20JDAMs%20to%20Israel%2C%20notwithstanding%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20somewhat%20disingenuous%20claim%20that%20Tel%20Aviv%20was%20%E2%80%98losing%20international%20legitimacy%E2%80%99%20for%20what%20he%20termed%20its%20%E2%80%98indiscriminate%20bombings%E2%80%99.%20Other%20senior%20US%20officials%20also%20duplicitously%20iterated%20IDF%E2%80%99s%20preposterous%20assertions%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98doing%20everything%E2%80%99%20to%20reduce%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20its%20ongoing%20Gaza%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20CNN%20revealed%20that%20the%20remaining%2055%25%20or%20so%20of%20ordnance%20used%20by%20the%20IDF%20in%20its%20unchallenged%20bombing%20were%20the%20even%20more%20destructive%20precision%20guided%20munitions%20(PGMs)%20that%20included%202%2C000-pound%20bombs%20guided%20by%20%E2%80%98Smart%2C%20Precise%2C%20Cost-Effective%E2%80%99%20or%20SPICE%20kits%2C%20equipped%20with%20GPS%20guidance%20systems%20for%20greater%20accuracy.%20It%20reported%20recently%20that%20the%20US%20planned%20on%20transferring%20%24320%20million%20worth%20of%20SPICE%20kits%20to%20Israel%2C%20manufactured%20by%20the%20US%20subsidiary%20of%20Raphael%20Advanced%20Defence%20Systems%20in%20Haifa%20that%20originally%20developed%20these%20precision%20enablers%20for%20assorted%20air-to-ground%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%E2%80%99s%20Mirage%202000Hs%20which%20conducted%20the%20punitive%20raid%20on%20an%20alleged%20Islamist%20terrorist%20camp%20in%20Balakot%20in%20north-west%20Pakistan%20in%20February%202019%20%E2%80%93%20in%20response%20to%20the%20fatal%20bombing%20of%20a%20bus%20carrying%20Indian%20paramilitaries%20in%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%93%20also%20employed%20Israel-supplied%20SPICE%20kits%20to%20deliver%20Paveway%20II%20laser-guided%20bombs%20to%20their%20intended%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20disagreeable%20flashback%20to%20the%20second%20world%20war%20Dresden%20raids%2C%20Israel%2C%20like%20the%20RAF%20and%20the%20RAAF%2C%20also%20resorted%20to%20air%20dropping%20Arabic%20leaflets%20into%20Gazan%20towns%2C%20warning%20Palestinian%20civilians%20to%20vacate%20their%20homes%20ahead%20of%20impending%20bombing%20raids.%20And%20much%20like%20the%20former%2C%20the%20IDF%20leaflets%20too%20announced%20their%20unambiguous%20intent%20to%20carry%20out%20aerial%20strikes%2C%20warning%20all%20Gaza%20residents%20against%20disregarding%20these%20warnings%20at%20their%20peril.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dresden%20leaflets%20as%20paraphrased%20by%20American%20satirist%20Kurt%20Vonnegut%20Jr.%20%E2%80%93%20who%2C%20as%20a%20US%20army%20prisoner%20of%20war%20was%20interned%20in%20the%20city%20during%20its%20bombing%20and%20survived%20in%20a%20meat%20locker%20in%20a%20local%20slaughterhouse%20%E2%80%93%20starkly%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdestruction%20of%20anything%20other%20than%20military%20objectives%20was%20unintentional%20and%20the%20unavoidable%20fortunes%20of%20war%E2%80%9D.%20After%20the%20war%2C%20Vonnegut%20wrote%20%3Cem%3ESlaughterhouse-Five%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20semi-autobiographical%20anti-war%20novel%20of%20Dresden%E2%80%99s%20fire-bombing%20by%20the%20Allies%20that%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20best-seller%20in%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20little%20seems%20to%20have%20changed%20since%201945%20in%20the%20five%20basic%20principles%20governing%20the%20legal%20use%20of%20force%20by%20the%20powerful%20in%20an%20armed%20conflict.%20These%20incorporate%20military%20necessity%2C%20distinction-whereby%20attackers%20need%20to%20distinguish%20between%20combatants%20and%20civilians-proportionality%2C%20humanity%20and%20honour%20or%20chivalry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20it%20appears%20existed%20then%2C%20and%20certainly%20none%20do%20now%2C%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703764820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_Anti-Israel_Protest_Washington_DC_USA_01949_32857528933.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-has-outdone-its-backers-the-us-and-britain-in-reducing-cities-to-rubble%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Little%20seems%20to%20have%20changed%20since%201945%20in%20the%20five%20basic%20principles%20governing%20the%20legal%20use%20of%20force%20by%20the%20powerful%20in%20an%20armed%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-has-outdone-its-backers-the-us-and-britain-in-reducing-cities-to-rubble%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20driver%20who%20fled%20UK%20after%20crash%20left%20nurse%20unable%20to%20walk%20gears%20up%20for%20legal%20fight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703764500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-issac-calderon-texas-national-guard_6405908.jpg%3F20231228111810%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffather-of-us-driver-who-fled-uk-after-crash-left-nurse-unable-to-walk-sets-up-fundraising-page-for-legal-fight-13038630%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20father%20of%20an%20American%20driver%20who%20fled%20the%20UK%20after%20a%20crash%20left%20a%20British%20nurse%20unable%20to%20walk%20is%20attempting%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20his%20son's%20legal%20costs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A161%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffather-of-us-driver-who-fled-uk-after-crash-left-nurse-unable-to-walk-sets-up-fundraising-page-for-legal-fight-13038630%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffather-of-us-driver-who-fled-uk-after-crash-left-nurse-unable-to-walk-sets-up-fundraising-page-for-legal-fight-13038630%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffather-of-us-driver-who-fled-uk-after-crash-left-nurse-unable-to-walk-sets-up-fundraising-page-for-legal-fight-13038630%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Weather%20event%20that%20caused%20'Beast%20from%20the%20East'%20forecast%20to%20strike%20northern%20Europe%20in%20January%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703763420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-beast-east-2018-snow_6406181.jpg%3F20231228162019%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsudden-stratospheric-warming-forecast-to-hit-northern-europe-in-january-but-experts-unsure-where-it-will-strike-13038622%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK%20could%20find%20itself%20in%20the%20deep%20freeze%20in%20January%20due%20to%20a%20change%20in%20wind%20patterns%20high%20up%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20-%20the%20same%20phenomenon%20that%20blew%20in%20the%20bitterly%20cold%20Beast%20from%20the%20East%20in%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A329%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fsudden-stratospheric-warming-forecast-to-hit-northern-europe-in-january-but-experts-unsure-where-it-will-strike-13038622%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsudden-stratospheric-warming-forecast-to-hit-northern-europe-in-january-but-experts-unsure-where-it-will-strike-13038622%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fsudden-stratospheric-warming-forecast-to-hit-northern-europe-in-january-but-experts-unsure-where-it-will-strike-13038622%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pegasus%20Used%20to%20Target%20The%20Wire's%20Founding%20Editor%2C%20Reporter%20Working%20on%20Adani%2C%20Amnesty%20Confirms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F02143130%2Fpegasus397131.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%20says%20it%20has%20detected%20evidence%20that%20Pegasus%20spyware%20was%20used%20by%20an%20unknown%20government%20agency%20to%20compromise%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20two%20journalists%20in%20India%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Anand%20Mangnale%20of%20the%20Oraganised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20released%20its%20findings%20on%20December%2028%20as%20part%20of%20its%20partnership%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2F2023.12.28-021126%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F12%2F27%2Findia-apple-iphone-hacking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20wider%20investigation%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20Varadarajan%20has%20been%20targeted%20with%20the%20Israeli%20made%20spyware.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%202021%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20by%20a%20worldwide%20media%20consortium%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Pegasus%20Project%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20phone%20was%20among%20several%20other%20journalists%2C%20opposition%20politicians%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%20on%20whose%20devices%20Amnesty%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%20found%20Pegasus.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20spyware%20on%20Magnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%20is%20especially%20concerning%20as%20the%20trigger%20for%20his%20selection%20as%20a%20target%20appears%20to%20be%20his%20investigation%20into%20the%20business%20affairs%20of%20the%20Adani%20group.%20As%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Aug.%2023%2C%20the%20OCCRP%20emailed%20Adani%20seeking%20comment%20for%20a%20story%20it%20would%20publish%20a%20week%20later%20alleging%20that%20his%20brother%20was%20part%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eof%20a%20group%20that%20had%20secretly%20traded%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20public%20stock%2C%20possibly%20in%20violation%20of%20Indian%20securities%20law.%20A%20forensic%20analysis%20of%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20conducted%20by%20Amnesty%20International%20and%20shared%20with%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%2C%20found%20that%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20that%20inquiry%2C%20an%20attacker%20infiltrated%20the%20device%20and%20planted%C2%A0Pegasus%2C%20the%20notorious%20spyware%C2%A0that%20was%20developed%20by%20Israeli%20company%20NSO%20Group%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eand%20that%20NSO%20says%20is%20sold%20only%20to%20governments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20latest%20findings%20show%20that%20increasingly%2C%20journalists%20in%20India%20face%20the%20threat%20of%20unlawful%20surveillance%20simply%20for%20doing%20their%20jobs%2C%20alongside%20other%20tools%20of%20repression%20including%20imprisonment%20under%20draconian%20laws%2C%20smear%20campaigns%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20intimidation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Donncha%20%C3%93%20Cearbhaill%2C%20head%20of%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20said%20its%20Security%20Lab%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20observed%20indications%20of%20renewed%20Pegasus%20spyware%20threats%20towards%20individuals%20in%20India%20during%20a%20regular%20technical%20monitoring%20exercise%20in%20June%202023%2C%20a%20number%20of%20months%20after%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20seeking%20to%20procure%20a%20new%20commercial%20spyware%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Apple%20issued%20threat%20notifications%20globally%20to%20iPhone%20users%20who%20may%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%2C%20Varadarajan%2C%20Mangnale%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20journalists%20and%20opposition%20politicians%20in%20India%20received%20the%20notifications.%20Among%20those%20who%20went%20public%20at%20the%20time%20were%20Mahua%20Moitra%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20a%20prominent%20critic%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Nair%2C%20a%20journalist%20with%20OCCRP%20who%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Adani%20story%20with%20Mangnale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%20undertook%20a%20forensic%20analysis%20on%20the%20phones%20of%20Varadarajan%20and%20Mangnale%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20traces%20of%20Pegasus%20spyware%20activity%20on%20devices%20owned%20by%20both%20Indian%20journalists%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Security%20Lab%20recovered%20evidence%20from%20Anand%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20device%20of%20a%20zero-click%20exploit%20which%20was%20sent%20to%20his%20phone%20over%20iMessage%20on%2023%20August%202023%2C%20and%20designed%20to%20covertly%20install%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware.%20The%20phone%20was%20running%20iOS%2016.6%2C%20the%20latest%20version%20available%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20zero-click%20exploit%20refers%20to%20malicious%20software%20that%20enables%20spyware%20to%20be%20installed%20on%20a%20device%20without%20requiring%20any%20user%20action%20from%20the%20target%2C%20such%20as%20clicking%20on%20a%20link.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Security%20Lab%20also%20identified%20an%20attacker-controlled%20email%20address%20used%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Pegasus%20attack%20on%20his%20device.%20The%20recovered%20samples%20are%20consistent%20with%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20BLASTPASS%20exploit%2C%20publicly%20identified%20by%20Citizen%20Lab%20in%20September%202023%20and%20patched%20by%20Apple%20in%20iOS%2016.6.1%20(CVE-2023-41064).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAnand%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%20was%20vulnerable%20to%20this%20zero-click%20exploit%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20attack.%20It%20is%20currently%20unclear%20if%20the%20exploit%20attempt%20resulted%20in%20a%20successful%20compromise%20of%20his%20device.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Varadarajan%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20Amnesty%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsecuritylab.amnesty.org%2Flatest%2F2023%2F12%2Fpegasus-zero-click-exploit-threatens-journalists-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforensic%20report%20notes%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Security%20Lab%20reviewed%20forensic%20records%20from%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%E2%80%99s%20iPhone%2011%20and%20identified%20traces%20which%20confirms%20that%20his%20phone%20was%20also%20target%20with%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHomeKit%20logs%20from%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20iPhone%20show%20that%20the%20was%20also%20targeted%20by%20the%20same%20Pegasus%20attacker%20email%20account%20used%20to%20target%20Anand%20Mangnale.%20The%20recovered%20HomeKit%20logs%20show%20that%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Enatalymarinova%40proton.me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Apple%20account%20interacted%20with%20his%20device%E2%80%99s%20HomeKit%20service%20on%2016%20October%202023%20around%2014%3A36%3A09%20UTC.%20At%20the%20time%20his%20phone%20was%20running%20iOS%20version%2016.6.1%20which%20was%20not%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20BLASTPAST%20attack.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20iVerify%2C%20a%20New%20York%20security%20firm%20it%20engaged%20to%20test%20the%20phones%20of%20some%20of%20the%20Indian%20politicians%20on%20the%20list%20of%20those%20who%20received%20a%20spyware%20alert%20from%20Apple%2C%20found%20tell-tale%20footprints%20of%20targetting%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIVerify%20examined%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20phone%20backup%20and%20confirmed%20that%20she%20had%20received%20an%20Apple%20warning.%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3EIt%20also%20saw%20urgent%20crash%20reports%20that%2C%20together%20with%20other%20digital%20records%2C%20suggested%20the%20device%20had%20been%20hacked.%20The%20company%20also%20found%20a%20threat%20notification%20and%20suspicious%20activity%20on%20the%20phone%20of%20Praveen%20Chakravarty%2C%20head%20of%20the%20opposition%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20data%20analytics%20department.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20renewed%20evidence%20of%20Pegasus%20being%20used%20against%20journalists%20in%20India%20comes%20more%20than%20a%20year%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20the%20technical%20committee%20it%20had%20appointed%20to%20probe%20allegations%20of%20illegal%20surveillance%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-pegasus-technical-committee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20evidence%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmalware%E2%80%99%20in%20as%20many%20as%20five%20mobile%20phones%20which%20it%20tested%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20then%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%2C%20N.V.%20Ramana%2C%20had%20also%20said%20that%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20had%20refused%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20court%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20technical%20committee%20was%20created%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20confirm%20or%20deny%20its%20purchase%20and%20use%20of%20Pegasus%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20held%20the%20government%20in%20contempt%20and%20has%20also%20not%20taken%20any%20further%20action%20on%20the%20findings%20it%20has.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20itself%20was%20not%20made%20public%2C%20citing%20privacy%20concerns%2C%20though%20some%20of%20the%20journalists%20who%20had%20submitted%20their%20devices%20for%20testing%20had%20said%20they%20had%20no%20objection%20to%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20being%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPressure%20on%20Apple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cem%3E%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20also%20documents%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20control%20the%20narrative%20soon%20after%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20October%20notiications%20were%20issued%2C%20which%20included%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20executives%20in%20India%20to%20themselves%20downplay%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20warning%20they%20had%20just%20issued%20to%20iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22article-body%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSenior%20Modi%20administration%20officials%20called%20Apple%20India%E2%80%99s%20managing%20director%2C%20Virat%20Bhatia%2C%20after%20the%20news%20broke%2C%20said%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter.%20One%20of%20the%20people%20said%20Indian%20officials%20asked%20Apple%20to%20withdraw%20the%20warnings%20and%20say%20it%20had%20made%20a%20mistake.%20After%20a%20heated%20discussion%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20India%20office%20said%20the%20most%20it%20could%20do%20was%20put%20out%20a%20public%20statement%20that%20emphasized%20certain%20caveats%20that%20Apple%20had%20already%20listed%20on%20its%20tech%20support%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2Fo%2FtjMEN%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-in%2F102174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epage%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eabout%20the%20warnings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703763294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F02143130%2Fpegasus397131.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpegasus-used-to-target-the-wires-founding-editor-reporter-working-on-adani-amnesty-confirms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20OCCRP%20sent%20queries%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20on%20August%2024%20and%20%26quot%3Bwithin%2024%20hours%20of%20that%20inquiry%2C%20an%20attacker%20infiltrated%20the%20device%20and%20planted%C2%A0Pegasus%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20phone%20of%20its%20reporter%2C%20Anand%20Mangnale%2C%20the%20Washington%20Post%20and%20Amnesty%20International%20have%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpegasus-used-to-target-the-wires-founding-editor-reporter-working-on-adani-amnesty-confirms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%20Court%20Commutes%20Indian%20Navy%20Veterans'%20Death%20Sentence%20to%20Prison%20Terms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24160310%2FCourt-of-appeals.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Two%20months%20after%20sentencing%20eight%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans%20to%20death%2C%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20reduced%20their%20capital%20punishment%20to%20imprisonment%20of%20varying%20terms%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2028).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20noted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cverdict%20today%20of%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20of%20Qatar%20in%20the%20Dahra%20Global%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20sentences%20have%20been%20reduced%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20that%20Vipul%2C%20the%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20Qatar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20veterans%E2%80%99%20family%20members%20were%20present%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20when%20the%20order%20was%20delivered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20a%20detailed%20judgement%20is%20awaited%2C%20the%20MEA%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20close%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%20as%20well%20as%20the%20family%20members%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20steps%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20usual%2C%20the%20ministry%20explained%20that%20it%20would%20not%20make%20any%20further%20comments%20at%20this%20juncture%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20confidential%20and%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20proceedings%20of%20this%20case%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20stood%20by%20them%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20extend%20all%20consular%20and%20legal%20assistance.%20We%20will%20also%20continue%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20Qatari%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20veterans%E2%80%99%20sentences%20were%20reduced%2C%20but%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20they%20have%20been%20given%20varying%20prison%20terms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20eight%20men%20are%20Captain%20Navtej%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20Captain%20Birendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Vasisht%2C%20Commodore%20Amit%20Nagpal%2C%20Commodore%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20Commodore%20Sugunakar%20Pakala%2C%20Commodore%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Sailor%20Ragesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20handed%20the%20death%20penalty%20to%20the%20veterans%2C%20who%20had%20been%20detained%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEmployed%20by%20the%20now-defunct%20Omani%20private%20firm%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20they%20were%20contracted%20for%20providing%20training%20and%20related%20services%20to%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20charges%20have%20never%20been%20made%20public%2C%20media%20reports%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20being%20charged%20with%20espionage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20October%20verdict%2C%20but%20had%20even%20then%20refrained%20from%20making%20further%20comments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20four%20weeks%20later%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-court-accepts-appeal-application-against-death-sentence-to-8-indian-navy-veterans%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccepted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20deliberations%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20against%20the%20veterans%E2%80%99%20death%20sentence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%20party%20expressed%20relief%20with%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeals%E2%80%99%20decision%20in%20Qatar%20to%20reduce%20the%20death%20penalty%20for%20eight%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans.%20The%20party%20expressed%20hope%20that%20not%20only%20will%20their%20jail%20sentences%20be%20overturned%20but%20also%20that%20they%20will%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20shares%20its%20immediate%20relief%20along%20with%20the%20entire%20nation%20that%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20in%20Qatar%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20death%20penalty%20on%208%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20officers.%20While%20fuller%20details%20are%20awaited%20we%20express%20the%20hope%20that%20even%20the%20jail%20sentence%20that%20has%20replaced%20the%20death%20penalty%20will%20be%20set%20aside%20and%20the%20officers%20will%20be%20set%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1740338336416301250%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20commutation%20of%20their%20death%20sentences%2C%20the%20eight%20Indians%20become%20eligible%20for%20repatriation%20to%20India%20under%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fnews_updates%2Flist-of-agreements-mous-exchanged-by-external-affairs-minister-and-her-qatari-counterpart-dr-khalid-bin-mohammed-al-attiyah-during-the-visit-of-emir-of-qatar-to-india%2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fnews_updates%2Flist-of-agreements-mous-exchanged-by-external-affairs-minister-and-her-qatari-counterpart-dr-khalid-bin-mohammed-al-attiyah-during-the-visit-of-emir-of-qatar-to-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3E2015%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0bilateral%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D112436%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Fnewsite%2FPrintRelease.aspx%3Frelid%3D112436%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eagreement%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20sentenced%20persons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20prisoners%20to%20serve%20their%20sentence%20in%20their%20home%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703763283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24160310%2FCourt-of-appeals.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-court-commutes-death-sentence-given-to-eight-indian-navy-veterans%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20said%20it%20would%20not%20make%20any%20further%20comments%20at%20this%20juncture%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20confidential%20and%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20proceedings%20of%20this%20case%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%2