n%3Cp%3EIt%20cited%20officials%20as%20saying%20that%20those%20from%20the%20state%20who%20did%20not%20return%20to%20India%20on%20Tuesday%20(December%2026)%20may%20be%20among%20those%20who%20have%20sought%20asylum%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20relative%20of%20one%20of%20the%20returnees%20from%20Punjab%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20passenger%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fseparate-probes-on-post-plane-grounding-in-france-over-trafficking-suspicions-101703740328032.html%5C%22%3Epaid%20Rs%204%20lakh%20to%20an%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20him%20reach%20the%20US%20via%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20next%20installment%20was%20to%20be%20paid%20when%20he%20would%20have%20reached%20Nicaragua%20and%20another%20after%20reaching%20Mexico%20and%20the%20final%20one%20on%20reaching%20the%20final%20destination%20%5Bthe%20US%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20passenger%E2%80%99s%20relative%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20reported%20a%20Gujarat%20police%20officer%20as%20saying%20that%20officials%20found%20all%20passengers%20from%20the%20state%20to%20be%20carrying%20legal%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-probes-suspected-human-trafficking-after-276-nationals-return-home-2023-12-27%2F%5C%22%3E303%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20including%2011%20unaccompanied%20minors%20%E2%80%93%20were%20aboard%20the%20flight%20when%20it%20left%20the%20UAE%20for%20Nicaragua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20stopped%20to%20refuel%20at%20the%20Vatry%20airport%20near%20Paris%2C%20where%20it%20was%20grounded%20by%20local%20authorities%20who%20said%20they%20received%20a%20tip-off%20indicating%20that%20victims%20of%20human%20trafficking%20may%20have%20been%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20remained%20there%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F12%2F26%2Findians-sent-back-by-france-over-trafficking-concerns-what-we-know%5C%22%3Efor%20four%20days%20amid%20legal%20deliberations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20passengers%2C%20including%20five%20minors%2C%20applied%20for%20asylum%20in%20France%20and%20remain%20there%20as%20of%20Thursday%20(December%2028)%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20passengers%20were%20designated%20by%20French%20authorities%20as%20%E2%80%9Cassisted%20witnesses%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20status%20intermediate%20between%20that%20of%20witnesses%20and%20indicted%20suspects%20%E2%80%93%20after%20they%20were%20investigated%20for%20suspected%20people%20smuggling%2C%20Reuters%E2%80%99s%20report%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20told%20the%20AFP%20news%20agency%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20a%20local%20judge%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Fnews%2F25-indian-passengers-from-plane-held-in-france-freed-3e251718%3Frefsec%3Dtopics_afp-news%5C%22%3Ereleased%20the%2025%20asylum%20seekers%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20technical%20grounds.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20therefore%20free%20to%20do%20as%20they%20please%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20in%20an%20irregular%20situation%20on%20French%20territory%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20quoted%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20added%20that%20the%20charge%20of%20human%20trafficking%20was%20dropped%20after%20it%20was%20established%20that%20the%20passengers%20boarded%20the%20flight%20of%20their%20own%20free%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20why%20the%20flight%20landed%20in%20Mumbai%20instead%20of%20proceeding%20to%20Nicaragua%20from%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20France%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaembFrance%2Fstatus%2F1739292993717186788%5C%22%3Ethanking%20the%20French%20government%20and%20the%20Vatry%20airport%3C%2Fa%3E%20f